  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThe current implementation mixes the RPC commands with the lower level libp2p protocol. This was originally done to perform the SSZ decoding as we receive packets. \r\n\r\nIt is cleaner and has better logic separation to perform the decoding and RPC logic in its own module which deals with the associated functions, separating it from the networking stack.\r\n\r\nThis needs a re-write and re-design.\r\n",
